{"ID":270367, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"367\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs366.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs368.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 367<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">me shall see it, and know that I testify the truth concerning them.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Resurrection Universal<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">In regard to the law of the Priesthood,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> there should be a place where all nations shall come up<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span>\n  from time to time to receive their endowments;<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> and the Lord has said this shall be the place for the\n  baptisms for the dead.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> Every man that has been baptized and belongs to the kingdom has a right to\n  be baptized for those who have gone before; and as soon as the law of the Gospel<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> is obeyed here\n  by their friends who act as proxy for them, the Lord has administrators there to set them free.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> A man\n  may act as proxy for his own relatives; the ordinances of the Gospel which were laid out before the\n  foundations of the world<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> have thus been fulfilled by them, and we may be baptized for those whom\n  we have much friendship for; but it must first be revealed to the man of God,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> lest we should run too\n  far.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> &ldquo;As in Adam all die, even so in Christ shall all be made alive;&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> all shall be raised from the\n  dead.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> The Lamb of God hath brought to pass the resurrection,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> so that all shall rise from the\n  dead.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">God Almighty Himself dwells in eternal fire;<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> flesh and blood cannot go there,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> for all\n  corruption is devoured by the fire. &ldquo;Our God is a consuming fire.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> When our flesh is quickened\n  by the Spirit,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> there will be no blood in this tabernacle. Some dwell in higher glory than others.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Those who have done wrong always have that wrong gnawing them.<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> Immortality dwells in\n  everlasting burnings.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> I will from time to time reveal to you the subjects that are revealed by the\n  Holy Ghost to me.<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> All the lies<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> that are now hatched up<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> against me are of the devil,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> and the\n  influence of the devil and his servants will be used against the kingdom of God.<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span> The servants of\n  God<span class=\"footRef\">26<\/span> teach nothing but principles of eternal life, by their works ye shall know them.<span class=\"footRef\">27<\/span> A good man\n  will speak good things and holy principles, and an evil man evil things.<span class=\"footRef\">28<\/span> I feel, in the name of the\n  Lord, to rebuke all such bad principles, liars,<span class=\"footRef\">29<\/span> &amp;c., and I warn all of you to look out whom you are\n  going after. I exhort you to give heed to all the virtue and the teachings<span class=\"footRef\">30<\/span> which I have given you.\n  All men who are immortal dwell in everlasting burnings.<span class=\"footRef\">31<\/span> You cannot go anywhere but where God\n  can find you out.<span class=\"footRef\">32<\/span> All men are<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116403\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116403)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116403)\">D&amp;C 132:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107013\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107013)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107013)\">Isa. 2:2-3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107661\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107661)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107661)\">Micah 4:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115943\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115943)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115943)\">D&amp;C 124:27-42<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116097\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116097)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116097)\">D&amp;C 128:1-25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115959\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115959)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115959)\">D&amp;C 124:29-36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114872\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114872)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114872)\">D&amp;C 88:78<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115319\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115319)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115319)\">D&amp;C 104:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107282\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107282)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107282)\">Isa. 61:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116708\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116708)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href